STATE of North Carolina
v.
Somchoi NOORSOB No. 131P16-4 Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 23, 2017. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina. Somchoi Noonsab, for Noonsab, Somchoi. Somchoi Noorsob, for Noorsob, Somchoi.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 21st of February 2017 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 23rd of February 2017."
